[
    {
        "text": "ï»¿In late March, last year, 2016, I became a parent for the first time.",
        "startTime": 939,
        "endTime": 5853,
        "slowStartTime": 1559,
        "slowEndTime": 9004
    },
    {
        "text": "Like so many parents,...",
        "startTime": 7264,
        "endTime": 8143,
        "slowStartTime": 11046,
        "slowEndTime": 12440
    },
    {
        "text": "...I wondered how I was going to balance my work with my new role as parent.",
        "startTime": 8205,
        "endTime": 12221,
        "slowStartTime": 12457,
        "slowEndTime": 18556
    },
    {
        "text": "And in that moment, I remember that the statistic for the US's policy on maternity leave...",
        "startTime": 12762,
        "endTime": 18908,
        "slowStartTime": 19293,
        "slowEndTime": 28587
    },
    {
        "text": "...flashed through my mind.",
        "startTime": 19170,
        "endTime": 20271,
        "slowStartTime": 28905,
        "slowEndTime": 30631
    },
    {
        "text": "American women are currently entitled to 12 weeks' unpaid leave.",
        "startTime": 21137,
        "endTime": 25043,
        "slowStartTime": 31855,
        "slowEndTime": 37790
    },
    {
        "text": "American men are entitled to nothing.",
        "startTime": 25638,
        "endTime": 28243,
        "slowStartTime": 38607,
        "slowEndTime": 42590
    },
    {
        "text": "Somehow, we and every American parent were expected to be \"back to normal\" in under three months.",
        "startTime": 29408,
        "endTime": 36769,
        "slowStartTime": 44262,
        "slowEndTime": 55378
    },
    {
        "text": "Without income?",
        "startTime": 37561,
        "endTime": 38638,
        "slowStartTime": 56491,
        "slowEndTime": 58182
    },
    {
        "text": "I remember thinking to myself,...",
        "startTime": 39527,
        "endTime": 40795,
        "slowStartTime": 59440,
        "slowEndTime": 61418
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"If the practical reality of pregnancy is another mouth to feed in your home,...",
        "startTime": 40952,
        "endTime": 45527,
        "slowStartTime": 61578,
        "slowEndTime": 68515
    },
    {
        "text": "...and America is a country where most people are living paycheck to paycheck,...",
        "startTime": 45877,
        "endTime": 49775,
        "slowStartTime": 68965,
        "slowEndTime": 74888
    },
    {
        "text": "...how does 12 weeks' unpaid leave economically work?\"",
        "startTime": 50366,
        "endTime": 53385,
        "slowStartTime": 75699,
        "slowEndTime": 80303
    },
    {
        "text": "The truth is, for too many people, it doesn't.",
        "startTime": 54571,
        "endTime": 56719,
        "slowStartTime": 82007,
        "slowEndTime": 85303
    },
    {
        "text": "One in four American women go back to work two weeks after giving birth...",
        "startTime": 57428,
        "endTime": 62702,
        "slowStartTime": 86292,
        "slowEndTime": 94278
    },
    {
        "text": "...because they can't afford to take off any more time than that.",
        "startTime": 62808,
        "endTime": 65106,
        "slowStartTime": 94362,
        "slowEndTime": 97884
    },
    {
        "text": "That's 25 percent of American women.",
        "startTime": 65376,
        "endTime": 68287,
        "slowStartTime": 98214,
        "slowEndTime": 102656
    },
    {
        "text": "Equally disturbing, women who can afford to take a full 12 weeks...",
        "startTime": 69611,
        "endTime": 72891,
        "slowStartTime": 104567,
        "slowEndTime": 109561
    },
    {
        "text": "...often don't because it will mean incurring a \"motherhood penalty,\"...",
        "startTime": 72988,
        "endTime": 76405,
        "slowStartTime": 109632,
        "slowEndTime": 114832
    },
    {
        "text": "...meaning they will be perceived as less dedicated to their job...",
        "startTime": 76927,
        "endTime": 79821,
        "slowStartTime": 115540,
        "slowEndTime": 119956
    },
    {
        "text": "...and will be passed over for promotions and other career advancement.",
        "startTime": 80055,
        "endTime": 83322,
        "slowStartTime": 120233,
        "slowEndTime": 125208
    }
]